{"tid":1002002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★公投：34歲是廢人 Vs 60歲是中年","createTime":"2019-01-30T15:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T12:01:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80ddee8a3cdc16a540d4981697c685256dd66b92","tid":1002002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"34歲是廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n60歲是中年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">華為興衰在此一舉 任正非：過了34歲就是廢人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為公司被爆出辭退34歲以上程式員的消息，這些程式員都已經為公司工作了十多年。展程CEO陳羽翔被指獨吞股權，逼走一起創業七年的程式員伙伴，從時間上來算創業七年也恰巧是30多歲的年紀。任正非解釋道：30多歲的程式員不能熬夜，失去激情30多歲的程式員成本太高，性價比太低，30多歲的程式員在法律上有更多權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haixiaba.com%2Fn369413.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6ugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=041f95d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html</a>"},{"pid":"72b4c53ed719bd5ac9da5c8da8f1f7b848b4bed6","tid":1002002,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSQAOdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSQAOdh.jpg&h=7e1069fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5e56f4a8064e9d35545309e054aefd9bdf77744","tid":1002002,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067236eeeadf2f2497a85e374cced5ef1bd1e3f6","tid":1002002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ac0352fd999f2645069c73925ac9ee0f3a12533b","tid":1002002,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"綜援戶是否廢人"},{"pid":"e28e73c03fdf8071ba4dd6ed